wiki.content:
They sing about a girl that gets beaten up by her boyfriend and hides her wounds with make-up, but since she still loves her boyfriend, she sticks around even though she gets beaten, probably because she has hope for a change, but in the end, the boyfriend will have to learn that if he keeps acting like that, she will leave him. 
 
 The song was written by Winter about lead singer Ronnie Winter's mother who was abused by his father.
